          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2503-Step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> </strong>roughly</p><p>Heat a pot with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]<strong> </span>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until beginning to break down</p><p>Whilst the tomatoes are cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2503-Step-2-x200.jpg",
